==English==

=== Noun ===
'''thrush'''  (''plural:'' '''[[thrushes]]''')
# One of several species of songbirds often with spotted underbellies: [[Bluebird]]s, [[nightingale]]s, and [[robin]]s are all types of thrushes.
# A [[yeast]] infection of the mouth or urethra.

